snippet.title: Breach & Clear Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Breach & Clear, the upcoming tactical strategy game developed by Mighty Rabbit and published by Gun Media, is coming to the App Store on July 18th!

Get the game here! 
Apple App Store: https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/breach-clear/id655749677?mt=8 
Google Play: https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.gun.bnc 

www.facebook.com/breachandclear
www.twitter.com/BreachClearGame
www.Breachandclear.com
